.SH NAME
StorageAccessHandle.localStorage \- StorageAccessHandle: localStorage
property
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]localStorage\f[B]\f[R] property of the
\f[CR]StorageAccessHandle\f[R] interface returns an unpartitioned local
\f[CR]Storage\f[R] object if access was granted, and throws a
\f[CR]SecurityError\f[R] \f[CR]DOMException\f[R] otherwise.
.SH VALUE
A \f[CR]Storage\f[R] object.
.SH EXAMPLES
.IP
